Or:
```json
{
  "action": "wallet_archived",
  "payload": {
    "wallet_id": "uuid-123",
    "chain": "ethereum",
    "address": "0x...",
    "reason": "user_request"
  }
}
```

The `payload` is flexible JSON - different actions have different data structures. No rigid schema needed.

